      <alternative lang="ka.">na gaṇṭusakaraṇamattena</alternative>
    </alternatives>
    <type>auto</type>
    <previous> Evaṃ kho, bhikkhave, atthataṃ hoti kathinaṃ, evaṃ anatthataṃ. Kathañca pana, bhikkhave, anatthataṃ hoti kathinaṃ? Na ullikhitamattena atthataṃ hoti kathinaṃ, na dhovanamattena atthataṃ hoti kathinaṃ, na cīvaravicāraṇamattena </previous>
  </note>
